       <div class="od mainContent">
       <h1 class="aTitle">博恩科祝贺山东铸造年会圆满成功</h1>
       <h2 class="articleTime">添加时间:2023-04-06&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span>阅读次数:&nbsp;&nbsp;<script src="/index.php?c=article&a=hits&id=228" type="text/javascript"></script></span></h2>
       <div class="introduction nmt">
         <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 24px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.901961); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; letter-spacing: 0.544px; orphans: 2; white-space: normal; widows: 2; text-align: center; visibility: visible; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><img src="/uploads/editor/image/20230406/1680762343652098.jpg" title="1680762343652098.jpg" alt="微信图片_20230406102209.jpg"/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 24px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.901961); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; letter-spacing: 0.544px; orphans: 2; text-align: left; white-space: normal; widows: 2; visibility: visible; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-indent: 2em; visibility: visible; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">2023年3月31日-4月4日，2022年度山东省铸造年会在滨州隆重开幕，逾500代表齐聚一堂，共襄年度盛典。</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-indent: 2em; visibility: visible; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">本届年会以“高质·发展·科学·规范”为主题，在疫情后经济快速恢复的背景下，为铸造行业健康发展锚定目标、规划路线。</span></p><p style="text-align:center"><img src="/uploads/editor/image/20230406/1680762350236779.jpg" title="1680762350236779.jpg" alt="微信图片_20230406140630.jpg"/></p><section style="margin: 0px 0px 24px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.901961); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; letter-spacing: 0.544px; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0em; white-space: normal; widows: 2; visibility: visible; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"></section><p style="text-align:center"><img src="/uploads/editor/image/20230406/1680762362404193.jpg" title="1680762362404193.jpg" alt="微信图片_20230406140638.jpg"/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 24px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.901961); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; letter-spacing: 0.544px; orphans: 2; white-space: normal; widows: 2; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 楷体; font-size: 14pt;">中国铸造协会常务副会长张志勇开幕式致辞</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 24px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.901961); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; letter-spacing: 0.544px; orphans: 2; white-space: normal; widows: 2; text-align: left; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 楷体; font-size: 14pt;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-indent: 34px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">会上，中国铸造协会张志勇常务副会长、山东省铸造协会张江秘书长分别进行了发言，对国内经济形势和行业发展态势进行分析，就当前行业政策进行了解读。</span></span></p><p style="text-align:center"><img src="/uploads/editor/image/20230406/1680762380243827.jpg" title="1680762380243827.jpg" alt="微信图片_202304061343451.jpg"/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 24px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.901961); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; letter-spacing: 0.544px; orphans: 2; white-space: normal; widows: 2; text-align: left; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="letter-spacing: 0.544px;">博恩科自动化受邀参加此次大会，旨在加快铸造企业智能制造步伐，提升标准供给质量，解决铸造企业打磨环节从业人员短缺等问题。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 24px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.901961); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; letter-spacing: 0.544px; orphans: 2; white-space: normal; widows: 2; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; text-align: left; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">通过自动化、数字化、智能化的自动打磨方式，更安全、更环保、更绿色、更低碳的解决铸件后处理的打磨难题。</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 24px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.901961); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; letter-spacing: 0.544px; orphans: 2; white-space: normal; widows: 2; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; text-align: left; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">为铸造企业降成本、提效率、保质量、减用工，实现打磨环节的转型升级，用数字技术、智能技术改造提升传统的铸件打磨方式。</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 24px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.901961); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; letter-spacing: 0.544px; orphans: 2; white-space: normal; widows: 2; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><img src="/uploads/editor/image/20230406/1680761533923621.jpg" title="1680761533923621.jpg" alt="微信图片_20230406134345.jpg" width="2574" height="881" style="width: 2574px; height: 881px;"/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 24px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.901961); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; letter-spacing: 0.544px; orphans: 2; white-space: normal; widows: 2; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; text-align: left; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: center; text-indent: 34px; font-size: 14pt;">3日，与会</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: center; text-indent: 34px; font-size: 14pt;">代表</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: center; text-indent: 34px; font-size: 14pt;">参观了</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: center; text-indent: 34px; font-size: 14pt;">滨州活</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: center; text-indent: 34px; font-size: 14pt;">塞有限公司、海纳川（</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: center; text-indent: 34px; font-size: 14pt;">滨州）轻量化汽车部件有限公司、山东国创精密机械有限公司、山东惠宇汽车零部件有限公司4家铸造企业，这些企业先进的生产技术水平和管理水平受到代表们一致称赞，值得相互学习借鉴，至此，山东铸造</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: center; text-indent: 34px; font-size: 14pt;">协会</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: center; text-indent: 34px; font-size: 14pt;">年会画上了圆满的句号。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 24px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.901961); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; letter-spacing: 0.544px; orphans: 2; white-space: normal; widows: 2; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br/></p><p><br/></p>         <div class="od articlePages">
